<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>I led the development of a custom portal for an enterprise client, enabling users to securely log in and raise requests to provision, modify, or delete Azure resources. The portal enforced client-specific design, naming conventions, and configuration standards, ensuring compliance and operational consistency. Approval workflows were integrated, triggering resource deployment only after validation by the concerned team.</p>

